text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 4.61.7, International Examination Guidelines, Controlled Foreign Corporations.

This IRM is obsolete, as the content is informational and not instructions to staff, in accordance with IRM 4.51.2, LB&I Administrative Guidance, Supplemental Guidance and Informational Resources. The International Knowledge Base provides informational resources for Controlled Foreign Corpora- tions (CFC) Income, under Business Outbound. Information can also be obtained by contacting the CFC Income Practice Network team.
EFFECT ON OTHER DOCUMENTS IRM 4.61.7 dated October 8, 2019 is obsolete.
